<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:12:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亲巴勒斯坦学生抗议者与西北大学达成协议以遏制抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-student-protesters-reach-deal-with-university-to-curb-protest-activity/0000018f-33a5-d8d8-a1ff-37f7b5a90000</link><description>与西北大学达成的协议将成立一个新的大学投资和其他承诺咨询委员会，让抗议活动持续到 6 月 1 日，但除了用于援助物资的帐篷外，禁止使用所有帐篷</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-student-protesters-reach-deal-with-university-to-curb-protest-activity/0000018f-33a5-d8d8-a1ff-37f7b5a90000</guid></item><item><title>报告：埃及停火提案中未包含以色列留在加沙的承诺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/report-israeli-commitment-to-stay-out-of-gaza-not-included-in-egypts-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-33c9-d8fb-a1df-bfef92500000</link><description>该提案详细说明，在协议第一阶段将释放 33 名人质，以换取以色列国防军从加沙大部分地区全面撤退并释放巴勒斯坦囚犯。加沙重建计划将在最后阶段实施</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/report-israeli-commitment-to-stay-out-of-gaza-not-included-in-egypts-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-33c9-d8fb-a1df-bfef92500000</guid></item><item><title>艾森科特抨击本-格维尔、斯莫特里奇：我不会加入一个根据政治议程做出决定的政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/eisenkot-blasts-ben-gvir-smotrich-i-wont-be-in-a-govt-that-bases-decisions-on-politics/0000018f-3386-d9c3-abcf-7bf774900000</link><description>这位战时内阁成员指责本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇勒索总理并危害国家安全。斯莫特里奇回答说：“这不是敲诈勒索，而是敲诈勒索。”这是数百万以色列人的合法意见</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/eisenkot-blasts-ben-gvir-smotrich-i-wont-be-in-a-govt-that-bases-decisions-on-politics/0000018f-3386-d9c3-abcf-7bf774900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者不满足于驱逐巴勒斯坦牧羊人，他们还偷走他们的羊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-settlers-arent-content-with-expelling-palestinians-they-also-steal-their-sheep/0000018f-2e83-d8c4-afef-2fff95bc0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，有关以色列定居者偷窃约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人牛群的报道不断增加。在一起案件中，盗窃发生在身穿制服的男子拘留并殴打牧羊人之后</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:18:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-settlers-arent-content-with-expelling-palestinians-they-also-steal-their-sheep/0000018f-2e83-d8c4-afef-2fff95bc0000</guid></item><item><title>谷歌员工因抗议与以色列签订的合同而被解雇，并向劳工监管机构提出投诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/google-workers-fired-for-protesting-israel-contract-file-complaint-with-labor-regulator/0000018f-3350-d8fb-a1df-bf76f0050000</link><description>数十名在谷歌办公室参加员工静坐后被解雇的谷歌员工向劳工监管机构提出投诉，称他们被“不公平解雇”，以试图夺回工作岗位</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/google-workers-fired-for-protesting-israel-contract-file-complaint-with-labor-regulator/0000018f-3350-d8fb-a1df-bf76f0050000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太作家保罗·奥斯特去世，享年 77 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/jewish-american-author-paul-auster-dies-aged-77/0000018f-3359-d215-afdf-7779b7430000</link><description>奥斯特的作品包括广受好评的小说，如《孤独的发明》、《机遇的音乐》和《4 3 2 1》。他在生命的最后几年一直在与癌症作斗争</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:31:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/jewish-american-author-paul-auster-dies-aged-77/0000018f-3359-d215-afdf-7779b7430000</guid></item><item><title>驱逐内塔尼亚胡会解决以色列的一切吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/will-ousting-netanyahu-solve-everything-for-israel/0000018f-3024-d8fb-a1df-bd667f600000</link><description>以色列政府国内外的反对者坚信内塔尼亚胡是一切错误的根源，从破坏民主到10月7日事件和加沙事件，除掉他将是解决以色列困境的灵丹妙药。讽刺的是，这种说法给了他太多的信任</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/will-ousting-netanyahu-solve-everything-for-israel/0000018f-3024-d8fb-a1df-bd667f600000</guid></item><item><title>“蔑视人的生命”：以色列人质的女儿抨击反对“为22或33人”停止加沙战争的极右翼部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/daughter-of-hostage-blasts-far-right-minister-opposed-to-stopping-war-for-22-or-33-people/0000018f-32f8-d8c4-afef-3ffcc8260000</link><description>宗教犹太复国主义党部长奥里特·斯特罗克(Orit Strock)在接受采访时表示，人质协议是“无伤大雅的”，并且“背离了战争的目标”。在受到人质亲属的批评后，斯特罗克回答说，“你不能取消这一观点的合法性，许多其他人也持有这种观点”</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:04:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/daughter-of-hostage-blasts-far-right-minister-opposed-to-stopping-war-for-22-or-33-people/0000018f-32f8-d8c4-afef-3ffcc8260000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在会见内塔尼亚胡时表示，哈马斯阻碍停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article-live/blinken-to-meet-netanyahu-hamas-demands-assurances-israel-wont-attack-gaza-for-months/0000018f-31ef-d8fb-a1df-bdef8d0a0000</link><description>报道：以色列谈判小组抵达开罗，提出哈马斯达成协议的要求 ■ 哈马斯消息人士：作为达成协议的条件，需要保证以色列在未来几个月内不会继续战斗 ■ 纽约警察局重新夺回哥伦比亚时，数十名亲巴勒斯坦抗议者被捕校园建筑</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article-live/blinken-to-meet-netanyahu-hamas-demands-assurances-israel-wont-attack-gaza-for-months/0000018f-31ef-d8fb-a1df-bdef8d0a0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约警察局夺回被占领的校园建筑后，数十名亲巴勒斯坦抗议者在哥伦比亚被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-pro-palestine-protestors-arrested-at-columbia-after-occupying-campus-building/0000018f-31e3-d9c3-abcf-7bf706fc0000</link><description>纽约警察局表示，所有闯入并占领常春藤盟校汉密尔顿大厅以抗议以色列对加沙地带哈马斯发动战争的学生均已被驱逐</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-pro-palestine-protestors-arrested-at-columbia-after-occupying-campus-building/0000018f-31e3-d9c3-abcf-7bf706fc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院维持因《古兰经》帖子“支持恐怖主义”而解雇穆斯林工程师的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-upholds-dismissal-of-muslim-engineer-over-terror-supporting-quran-posts/0000018f-3072-d278-a58f-ba7ad78a0000</link><description>蒙塔塞尔·阿巴西 (Muntaser Abbasi) 因将《古兰经》中的引述上传到他的 WhatsApp 状态而被解雇 - 法官裁定这“只能被理解为表达对恐怖主义的同情”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-upholds-dismissal-of-muslim-engineer-over-terror-supporting-quran-posts/0000018f-3072-d278-a58f-ba7ad78a0000</guid></item><item><title>世界法院驳回尼加拉瓜要求德国停止对以色列军事援助的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/world-court-rejects-nicaraguas-request-for-germany-to-halt-military-aid-to-israel/0000018f-3073-d8fb-a1df-bd77554d0000</link><description>尼加拉瓜声称以色列国防军正在利用德国军事援助进行加沙战争中违反国际法的行动，并要求法院立即发布临时禁令</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/world-court-rejects-nicaraguas-request-for-germany-to-halt-military-aid-to-israel/0000018f-3073-d8fb-a1df-bd77554d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔官员称以色列在拉法的行动将阻止人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/qatari-official-says-israeli-operation-in-rafah-would-prevent-hostage-deal/0000018f-307e-d9c3-abcf-7a7fbe070000</link><description>这位官员发表声明之前，内塔尼亚胡承诺“无论是否达成协议，我们都将进入拉法并摧毁那里的哈马斯营。”这是卡塔尔官员一周内第二次批评以色列破坏停火谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/qatari-official-says-israeli-operation-in-rafah-would-prevent-hostage-deal/0000018f-307e-d9c3-abcf-7a7fbe070000</guid></item><item><title>周二耶路撒冷老城发生刺伤事件后，以色列警察袭击巴勒斯坦旁观者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officers-assault-palestinian-bystanders-after-stabbing-attack-in-jerusalem/0000018f-3071-d0b5-a59f-31f5ad880000</link><description>希律门旁边广场上的一段视频显示，警察用脚踢并使用警棍殴打两名路过该地区的巴勒斯坦男子。警方称他们扰乱了警察，但没有拍摄到对抗的画面</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 19:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officers-assault-palestinian-bystanders-after-stabbing-attack-in-jerusalem/0000018f-3071-d0b5-a59f-31f5ad880000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：国际刑事法院对以色列领导人的逮捕令是“反犹太仇恨犯罪”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-icc-arrest-warrants-against-israeli-leaders-would-be-antisemitic-hate-crime/0000018f-3037-d0b5-a59f-31f78a070000</link><description>在有报道称国际刑事法院正在考虑向以色列官员发出逮捕令后，总理表示，任何事情“都不会影响我们实现战争所有目标的决心”。美国官员表示，如果国际刑事法院批准此举，他们将试图阻止此举</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 18:41:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-icc-arrest-warrants-against-israeli-leaders-would-be-antisemitic-hate-crime/0000018f-3037-d0b5-a59f-31f78a070000</guid></item><item><title>军方称，周日在加沙丧生的两名以色列国防军预备役人员死于友军火力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/two-idf-reservists-killed-in-gaza-on-sunday-died-from-friendly-fire-army-says/0000018f-2fee-d9c3-abcf-7fff8e7b0000</link><description>对军士长死亡的初步调查。 （res.）伊多·阿维夫和军士长。 （res.）卡尔基丹·梅哈里（Kalkidan Mehari）发现坦克乘员的错误识别导致了致命事件</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:26:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/two-idf-reservists-killed-in-gaza-on-sunday-died-from-friendly-fire-army-says/0000018f-2fee-d9c3-abcf-7fff8e7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 207 天：内塔尼亚胡表示以色列将进入拉法“无论有没有”人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-207-netanyahu-says-israel-will-enter-rafah-with-or-without-deal/0000018f-2ffd-d8fb-a1df-afff78260000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：无论有无协议，以色列都将进入拉法 ■ 土耳其公民在耶路撒冷刺伤以色列警察 ■ 外国外交官：沙特阿拉伯决定与以色列实现关系正常化，但正在权衡正式时间表 ■ 哥伦比亚大学暂停学生抗议者，一些人在汉密尔顿设置路障霍尔 ■ 战争进入 207 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-207-netanyahu-says-israel-will-enter-rafah-with-or-without-deal/0000018f-2ffd-d8fb-a1df-afff78260000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者在内塔尼亚胡总理家附近被捕，并被给予六个月的限制令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/protesters-arrested-near-pm-netanyahus-home-given-six-month-restraining-order/0000018f-2f94-d8c4-afef-2ffc72280000</link><description>抗议者在以色列总理位于凯撒利亚的私人官邸外被捕，法院裁定他们在六个月内不得进入距该建筑三公里范围内</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/protesters-arrested-near-pm-netanyahus-home-given-six-month-restraining-order/0000018f-2f94-d8c4-afef-2ffc72280000</guid></item><item><title>一位以色列作家讲述了 100 个 10 月 7 日故事，从两个小姐妹开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/an-israeli-writer-tells-100-october-7-stories-starting-with-two-young-sisters/0000018f-151c-d1f3-afcf-3f7dc1e90000</link><description>一个关于 10 月 7 日受害者的 Instagram 页面在网上疯传，一本包含 100 个当天事件的新书在法国引起轰动，萨拉·内塔尼亚胡 (Sara Netanyahu) 的一张经过处理的照片引发了一千个俏皮话</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:37:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/an-israeli-writer-tells-100-october-7-stories-starting-with-two-young-sisters/0000018f-151c-d1f3-afcf-3f7dc1e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长斯莫特里奇呼吁在“彻底消灭”加沙时“不采取半途而废的措施”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-calls-for-no-half-measures-in-the-total-annihilation-of-gaza/0000018f-2f4c-d9c3-abcf-7f7d25460000</link><description>以色列财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇在逾越节活动结束时发表讲话时还表示，目前与哈马斯的谈判“是在与一个很久以前就应该不复存在的人进行”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:07:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-calls-for-no-half-measures-in-the-total-annihilation-of-gaza/0000018f-2f4c-d9c3-abcf-7f7d25460000</guid></item></channel></rss>